=C2=A0
Would PDD=E2=80=99s $250B fall market cap still stand absent regulatory con=
cerns? Or is PDD still overvalued at $122B? Is it just kind of just like a =
Groupon for fruit? Groupon grew quickly too... before it fell just as fast.
Whether you=E2=80=99re a bull or a bear, Pinduoduo is an absolutely fascina=
ting company that has created, remixed, and popularized key innovations lik=
e team buying, =E2=80=9CInteractive Ecommerce,=E2=80=9D and Consumer-to-Man=
ufacturer (C2M). Fans argue that PDD brought the shopping mall to customers=
=E2=80=99 phones for the first time. No one can argue that its ascent from =
$0 to nearly $10 billion in revenue has been anything short of spectacular.=
 In the bullest of bull cases, it even has a shot at powering commerce in t=
